FORM CODE SPLITTING - COMPLETION NOTES
======================================

The main form code has been successfully split into logical smaller files:

FILES CREATED:
1. AmpMeasureForm.Main.cs - Main form class, constructor, utility methods
2. AmpMeasureForm.Designer.cs - Windows Forms Designer generated code [NEW]
3. AmpMeasureForm.Events.cs - Event handlers for menu items and form events
4. AmpMeasureForm.Grid.cs - DataGridView initialization and grid-related code
5. AmpMeasureForm.Columns.cs - Column width and order management
6. AmpMeasureForm.Data.cs - Data calculation and worksheet data models
7. AmpMeasureForm.SaveLoad.cs - File save/load operations
8. AmpMeasureForm.Theme.cs - Dark/light theme management
9. AmpMeasureForm.MRU.cs - Most Recently Used files functionality

KNOWN ISSUE TO FIX MANUALLY:
----------------------------
The AmpMeasureForm.resx file was created but is EMPTY, causing build errors.

TO FIX:
1. Close Visual Studio
2. Delete the empty AmpMeasure\AmpMeasureForm.resx file
3. Open the AmpMeasure\AmpMeasure.csproj file in a text editor
4. Remove these lines if they exist:
   <EmbeddedResource Include="AmpMeasureForm.resx">
     <DependentUpon>AmpMeasureForm.Main.cs</DependentUpon>
   </EmbeddedResource>

5. Save the .csproj file
6. Reopen Visual Studio and reload the solution
7. Open AmpMeasureForm.Main.cs in the designer view
8. Make a trivial change (like resizing the form slightly)
9. Save - this will regenerate the .resx file properly
10. Build the solution

ALTERNATIVE FIX:
---------------
If the above doesn't work, manually create the .resx file with this content:

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<root>
  <resheader name="resmimetype"><value>text/microsoft-resx</value></resheader>
  <resheader name="version"><value>2.0</value></resheader>
  <resheader name="reader"><value>System.Resources.ResXResourceReader, System.Windows.Forms, Version=4.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089</value></resheader>
  <resheader name="writer"><value>System.Resources.ResXResourceWriter, System.Windows.Forms, Version=4.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b77a5c561934e089</value></resheader>
  <metadata name="menuStrip1.TrayLocation" type="System.Drawing.Point, System.Drawing"><value>17, 17</value></metadata>
  <metadata name="statusStrip1.TrayLocation" type="System.Drawing.Point, System.Drawing"><value>132, 17</value></metadata>
  <metadata name="openFileDialog1.TrayLocation" type="System.Drawing.Point, System.Drawing"><value>248, 17</value></metadata>
  <metadata name="saveFileDialog1.TrayLocation" type="System.Drawing.Point, System.Drawing"><value>385, 17</value></metadata>
  <metadata name="autoSaveTimer.TrayLocation" type="System.Drawing.Point, System.Drawing"><value>522, 17</value></metadata>
</root>

After fixing the .resx file, the project should build successfully!
